Flow Design (Short)

1. Start


2. Input: Basic Salary, Worked Hours, Bonus Rate


3. If Worked Hours > 40, Input Overtime Bonus Rate


4. Calculate:

Extra Hours = Worked Hours - 40 (if any)

Bonus = Extra Hours × Bonus Rate

Gross Salary = Basic Salary + Bonus

Pension = Basic Salary × 0.07

Determine Tax Rate (based on Gross Salary)

Tax = Gross Salary × Tax Rate



5. Calculate:

Net Salary = Gross Salary - Pension - Tax



6. Output: Display Net Salary


7. End



